A11yPermission.checkBoxText: Aw bɛ taa ɲɛ ka yamaruya di kalo tilancɛ kɔnɔ ani aw kana nin finɛtiri in jira tugun .
A11yPermission.content: O baara in bɛ baarakɛcogo dɛmɛnan de wajibiya. N’i ​​b’a fɛ ka yamaruya di, i ka [OK] digi. N’i ​​b’a fɛ ka i dabila, i ka [Cancel] digi.
A11yPermission.title: yamaruyasɛbɛn baarakɛcogo .

floatPermission.checkBoxText: Aw bɛ taa ɲɛ ka yamaruya di kalo tilancɛ kɔnɔ ani aw kana nin finɛtiri in jira tugun .
floatPermission.content: O baara in bɛ ɲini ka yamaruya di finɛtiri baarakɛcogo ma min bɛ panpan. N’i ​​b’a fɛ ka yamaruya di, i ka [OK] digi. N’i ​​b’a fɛ ka i dabila, i ka [Cancel] digi.
